OL,7,FA teenager who needed life-saving
OL,8,Fsurgery after suffering a burst lung
OL,9,Fis warning others about the risk of
OL,10,Fvaping.
OL,12,FKyla Bright from Egremont in West
OL,13,FCumbria required surgery that lasted
OL,14,Ffive and a half hours after consuming
OL,15,Fa 4000 puff vape in a week.
OL,17,FShe is now warning others of the
OL,18,Fdangers.
