OL,3,CTeenager warns about the risk of
OL,4,Cvaping after needing life-saving
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FSpeaking on ITV's Good Morning
OL,8,FBritain, 17-year-old Kyla Bright said:
OL,9,F"I am okay now, definitely a lot
OL,10,Fbetter that what I was before.
OL,12,F"I was at my friends house and I
OL,13,Fpassed out but I passed out many times
OL,14,Fbefore so we didn't think anything of
OL,15,Fit.
OL,17,F"I then woke up the morning after and
OL,18,FI couldn't move comfortably, I could
OL,19,Fonly really be in one position without
OL,20,Fany pain. So walking about and stuff
OL,21,Fwas really difficult.
