OL,3,CTeenager warns about the risk of
OL,4,Cvaping after needing life-saving
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,F"I told my dad and he took me up to
OL,8,Fthe hospital where they knew there was
OL,9,Fsomething wrong and took me straight
OL,10,Fin.
OL,12,F"I had to then have an X-Ray straight
OL,13,Faway and then I had to have a drain
OL,14,Fput in to remove all of the air that
OL,15,Fhad collapsed in my lung. After that
OL,16,Fbecause the drain didn't work then I
OL,17,Fhad to have surgery."
OL,19,FThe teenager now says that she is put
OL,20,Foff the devices for life.
