OL,4,Cvaping after needing life-saving
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FWhen asked if there were any warning
OL,8,Fsigns for other people to look out
OL,9,Ffor, Kyla added: "I wouldn't know if
OL,10,Fit was a sign but I would be getting
OL,11,Fpain in my chest and then it would
OL,12,Feventually go away. I just didn't
OL,13,Freally think about it at first.
OL,15,F"Any time I would pick the vape up I
OL,16,Fwould always have quite a few puffs
OL,17,Fbefore I put it back down."
OL,19,FThe incident happened a couple of
OL,20,Fweeks ago with Kyla recently out of
OL,21,Fhospital.
