OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FKyla's dad, Mark, was previously a
OL,8,Fsmoker and then vaped but his
OL,9,Fdaughter's ordeal has turned him away
OL,10,Ffrom the devices.
OL,12,FHe said: "I was a heavy smoker and it
OL,13,Fwas absolutely fantastic this thing
OL,14,Fthat stopped me smoking.
OL,16,F"So to me it was brilliant but then
OL,17,Fthis happened and I have stopped all
OL,18,Ftogether now I don't vape at all.
